com.vdisk.net

类 ComplexUploadInputStreamEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • AbstractHttpEntity
      • com.vdisk.net.ComplexUploadInputStreamEntity

  • public class ComplexUploadInputStreamEntity
extends AbstractHttpEntity
    对上传文件流的封装。实现了对大文件的分段控制。 Encapsulation of upload input stream. To do the segmented control of big files.
    作者:
    Kevin
